{"word":"G4525 - σαίνω - saínō - sah'-ee-no - Move","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">saínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Move</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சலனப்படு"},{"paragraph":"1. to wag the tail"},{"paragraph":"2. to agitate, disturb, trouble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Akin to <a href=\"#/G4579 - σείω - seíō - si'-o/4579\">G4579</a>; to <i>wag</i> (as a dog its tail fawningly), that is, (generally) to <i>shake</i> (figuratively <i>disturb</i>): - move.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}